Italian life beckons six-year-old Vadodara orphan

TNN / Nov 03, 2019, 04:08 (IST)

“For I know the plans I have for you. Plans to prosper you, to give you hope and a future, declares the Lord” — reads Jeremiah 29:11. This couldn’t have been more truer but for a six-year-old orphan, Krupali, who till now had the sishu gruh in Vadodara as her home.

Dan Trachtenberg in talks to direct new 'Predator' film

ANI / Feb 11, 2024, 11:20 (IST)

Filmmaker Dan Trachtenberg, known for '10 Cloverfield Lane', is returning to the Predator franchise with a new film titled 'Badlands'. The film will have a female lead and is set to start production in July. Trachtenberg's previous film 'Prey' was a streaming success on Hulu.

Old video on a 'compulsory' vaccination program going viral; social media users establish COVID link

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Apr 17, 2023, 15:14 (IST)

An old video from “Conspiracy Theory with Jesse Ventura” is going viral in which Dr Lima Raibow talks about mass vaccination drive aiming at sterility.

Comedian Mann will lead AAP in Lok Sabha

TNN / Apr 22, 2015, 01:20 (IST)

As an expected fallout of the brawl in AAP, Patiala MP Dharam Vira Gandhi — who had raised his voice against the treatment meted out to Yogendra Yadav and Prashant Bhushan— was removed as the party’s leader in Lok Sabha on Tuesday. In his place, the party appointed stand-up comedian and Sangrur MP Bhagwant Mann to articulate its views in the lower House.

Sangrur MP Bhagwant Mann replaces Dharam Vira Gandhi as AAP leader in Lok Sabha

TNN / Apr 22, 2015, 07:20 (IST)

The Patiala MP gave considerable grief to Arvind Kejriwal and his aides when he endorsed the version of Bhushan and Yadav that the dominant faction resorted to strong-arm methods to intimidate dissidents and stifle their protest.
